.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH network 1  "network " 
.SH NAME
network \- Network connectivity utilities
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBnetwork\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Network connectivity utilities
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
network\-create(1)
Create a named network
.TP
network\-ls(1)
List networks or inspect one
.TP
network\-join(1)
Join a network from an invitation
.TP
network\-leave(1)
Leave a network
.TP
network\-invite(1)
Generate a network invitation
.TP
network\-kick(1)
Remove a device from a network
.TP
network\-test\-relay(1)
Test a Syncthing relay TCP connection
.TP
network\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
